            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing Phelia, Exuberant Shepherd as the commander in an aggressive manner to quickly overwhelm opponents. It includes a mix of low-cost creatures, disruption spells, and protection tools to maintain board control and pressure the opponent. Cards like Elite Spellbinder, Skyclave Apparition, and Mother of Runes help to disrupt the opponent's strategy, while cards like Blade Splicer and Stoneforge Mystic provide additional threats and value. The deck also includes removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Oust to deal with threats efficiently. Overall, the key concept of the deck is to apply early pressure, disrupt the opponent's game plan, and maintain control of the battlefield to secure victory."
